of ectoplasm tethered to her by wispy, ectoplasmic
tendrils. If she manifests two lashes, she can wield them
both as light melee weapons, each dealing 1d6 points of
slashing damage (1d4 if the ectoplasmatist is Small) with
a critical threat range and multiplier of 19–20/×2. If the
