fully manifested), it grants her a +2 bonus on saving
throws against the spell-like and supernatural abilities
of fey, outsiders, and incorporeal undead. At 6th level and
every 6 levels thereafter, this bonus increases by 1 (to a
maximum of +5 at 18th level). This ability replaces shared
consciousness and fused consciousness.
